quran[9{c,v,t}:
14,25,har aan woh apne rab ke hukum se apne phal day raha hai yeh misalein Allah is liye deta hai ke log inn se sabaq len
14,26,"aur kalma khabisa ki misaal aik bad zaat darakht ki si hai jo zameen ki satah se ukhaar phenka jata hai, uss ke liye koi istehkaam nahi hai"
14,27,"imaan laane walon ko Allah aik qoul saabit ki bunyaad par duniya aur akhirat, dono mein Sabaat ataa karta hai, aur zaalmon ko Allah bhatka deta hai Allah ko ikhtiyar hai jo chahay kere"
14,28,tum ne dekha unn logon ko jinhon ne Allah ki Nemat payi aur ussay kufran Nemat se badal dala aur ( apne sath ) apni qoum ko bhi halakat ke ghar mein jhonk diya
14,29,"yani jahannum, jis mein woh jhulsay jayen ge aur woh bad tareen jaye qarar hai"
14,30,"aur Allah ke kuch humsar tajweez kar liye taakay woh inhen Allah ke rastay se bhatka den inn se kaho, acha mazay kar lau, aakhir kaar tumhe palat kar jana dozakh hi mein hai"
14,31,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, mere jo bande imaan laaye hain unn se keh do ke namaz qaim karen aur jo kuch hum ne unn ko diya hai, uss mein se khulay aur chupay ( raah kher mein ) kharch karen qabal iss ke ke woh din aeye jis mein nah khareed o farokht hogi aur nah dost nawazi hosakay gi"
14,32,"Allah wohi to hai jis ne zameen aur asmano ko peda kya aur aasman se pani barsaya, phir is ke zareya se tumhari rizaq rasani ke liye terhan terhan ke phal peda kiye jis ne kashti ko tumahray liye maskhar kya ke samandar mein uss ke hukum se chalay aur daryaaon ko tumahray liye maskhar kya"
14,33,jis ne Sooraj aur chaand ko tumahray liye maskhar kya ke lagataar chalay ja rahay hain aur raat aur din ko tumahray liye maskhar kya
